Next, paint a cotton ball green and glue it to the top of the tree trunk. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/44/Make-a-Diorama-of-the-Civil-War-Step-4Bullet1.jpg/v4-459px-Make-a-Diorama-of-the-Civil-War-Step-4Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/44/Make-a-Diorama-of-the-Civil-War-Step-4Bullet1.jpg/v4-759px-Make-a-Diorama-of-the-Civil-War-Step-4Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":334,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":552.2527472527472,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
